245
00:14:53.159 --> 00:14:55.424
- Oh. my God. Is he okay?
- They didn't give any detail.

246
00:14:55.495 --> 00:14:57.139
They just told me to
come and pick him up.

247
00:14:57.163 --> 00:14:58.495
No. I'm going.

248
00:14:58.564 --> 00:15:00.226
Yeah. Helen. the
school called me.

249
00:15:00.299 --> 00:15:01.927
Yes. because it was
probably your fault.

250
00:15:02.001 --> 00:15:04.334
Please. That may be true.
but it's really important to me

251
00:15:04.404 --> 00:15:06.236
