Voice mail.

302
00:18:09.088 --> 00:18:10.920
- Fuck. Stacey. too.
- What?

303
00:18:11.190 --> 00:18:13.471
Do we know anyone on the
West Side who could pick them up?

304
00:18:13.826 --> 00:18:14.826
Um...

305
00:18:16.429 --> 00:18:18.625
Yeah. Uh. Brooklyn's mom.

306
00:18:22.034 --> 00:18:23.034
Good idea.

307
00:18:25.738 --> 00:18:28.606
Um. I'll pack a bag for the kids in
