know his grandparents.

323
00:19:09.448 --> 00:19:10.448
Thank you.

324
00:19:10.883 --> 00:19:12.511
Mm-hmm. I'll wait outside.

325
00:19:12.985 --> 00:19:14.453
Okay. be safe.

326
00:19:26.932 --> 00:19:28.696
