336
00:20:15.648 --> 00:20:18.379
Well. where did
they go? I... Yeah.

337
00:20:18.451 --> 00:20:21.615
Okay. I gotta... Yeah.
of course. Uh. bye.

338
00:20:21.887 --> 00:20:24.482
Um. Trevor and
Stacey weren't at school.

339
00:20:25.124 --> 00:20:25.955
