347
00:20:45.778 --> 00:20:48.145
I don't... I don't un... I
mean. no one's texted me.

348
00:20:48.214 --> 00:20:49.558
Anyone else who could
have picked them up?

349
00:20:49.582 --> 00:20:50.942
I don't know. I
mean. I-I don't...

350
00:20:50.983 --> 00:20:54.317
I have this. um... the-the
tracking app thingy.

351
00:20:54.386 --> 00:20:55.718
I don't... Can you do that?

352
00:20:55.788 --> 00:20:57.689
- Let me see.
- I've never used it.

353
00:20:58.324 --> 00:20:59.568
