359
00:21:15.441 --> 00:21:16.534
I mean. what the fuck?

360
00:21:21.046 --> 00:21:23.072
Hi. Do you have my kids?

361
00:21:25.417 --> 00:21:28.353
No. I don't want to FaceTime.
I don't want to FaceTime.

362
00:21:28.420 --> 00:21:32.585
<i>Hey. hey. I just want you
to see that your kids are fine.</i>

363
00:21:32.658 --> 00:21:33.956
<i>They're happy. safe.</i>

364
00:21:34.026 --> 00:21:36.894
<i>- Look. Hey. kids. say hi to your mother.</i>
- Hi. guys.

365
00:21:37.396 --> 00:21:38.659
- Look. Sasha.
<i>- Yes?</i>

366
00:21:38.731 --> 00:21:41.394
You cannot just get my
fucking kids without telling me.

367
00:21:41.467 --> 00:21:43.026
<i>I tried calling you.</i>

368
00:21:43.102 --> 00:21:45.196
<i>but your phone kept
going straight to voice mail.</i>

369
00:21:45.271 --> 00:21:49.003
<i>Listen. the city's gridlocked.
and-and I'm sending over a helicopter.</i>

370
00:21:49.074 --> 00:21:51.202
- You're sending a helicopter where?
<i>- To get you.</i>

371
00:21:51.277 --> 00:21:52.954
<i>Yeah. I've checked it
with my security guys.</i>

372
00:21:52.978 --> 00:21:55.573
<i>There's a landing pad just
up the hill from your house.</i>

373
00:21:55.648 --> 00:21:58.743
Yeah. I can't... I can't do that.
I have a house full of people.

374
00:21:58.818 --> 00:22:02.277
<i>Of course you do. What
else is new? So. who's there?</i>

375
00:22:02.354 --> 00:22:03.598
<i>Perhaps we can
squeeze them in. too.</i>

376
00:22:03.622 --> 00:22:04.622
Go. be with the kids.

377
00:22:06.559 --> 00:22:07.891
<i>- Is that Noah?</i>
- Yes!

378
00:22:07.960 --> 00:22:09.485
<i>What the fuck is he doing there?</i>

379
00:22:09.728 --> 00:22:11.439
<i>Helen. have you... have
