383
00:22:18.003 --> 00:22:21.405
<i>I just told you. your
kids are fine. Okay?</i>

384
00:22:21.473 --> 00:22:22.566
<i>They're doing great.</i>

385
00:22:22.641 --> 00:22:24.853
<i>But if you rather want to stay
