389
00:22:30.149 --> 00:22:31.447
<i>I suggest you get on it.</i>

390
00:22:34.820 --> 00:22:35.820
You should go.

391
00:22:40.559 --> 00:22:41.559
What about you?

392
00:22:41.660 --> 00:22:44.289
I'll be okay. I'm gonna
