436
00:25:45.344 --> 00:25:46.642
Well. I'm sorry. too.

437
00:25:49.081 --> 00:25:50.344
Yeah. okay.

438
00:25:52.451 --> 00:25:54.420
- Glass of wine?
- Yeah. please.

439
00:25:55.421 --> 00:25:56.421
All right.

440
00:25:57.322 --> 00:26:00.224
<i>Audrey Nelson is one of the
women accusing Solloway.</i>

441
00:26:00.292 --> 00:26:04.229
<i>We caught up with her this morning at
the annual Women in Media Breakfast.</i>

442
00:26:04.696 --> 00:26:07.325
<i>Yes. I was in his
